{"tid":549330,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"詭辯家的西西弗斯理論","createTime":"2018-02-03T13:31:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-03T13:48:53.000Z","uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"008226b524225f8720abbc424b0c8b6adad815bc","tid":549330,"uid":68626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:31:08.000Z","msg":"可能大家番工個陣就好想收工<br />\n可以去打機睇戲食飯買野行街<br />\n但係當打機睇戲食飯買野行街變左做工作個陣<br />\n你又會唔會好期待做依加自己做緊既工作<br />\n將佢當做娛樂<br />\n會唔會一樣叫春話第二日唔想番工?<br />\n其實大家唔想番工只係比自己番工呢個概念折磨緊<br />\n就好似西西弗斯比天神罰佢無限LOOP緊<br />\n大家只要將番工當放工 放工當番工<br />\n就可以唔洗覺得番工好痛苦了<br />\n利申 好鐘意番工<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b55f8a88df71514c9ba0f6786e41511227af7fc5","tid":549330,"uid":3063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:34:12.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/70gCdNUv6Vo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F70gCdNUv6Vo&d=l1IC3F0VMvIjKG%2BDrtaQI9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=d9d7bd0e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/70gCdNUv6Vo</a>"},{"pid":"469ceb25bcc209874c990c63ddb4814ff3e1c4fe","tid":549330,"uid":68081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-03T13:48:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/L8xy93I3hwk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FL8xy93I3hwk&d=l1IC3F0VMvIjKG%2BDrtaQI9U7RO4jIL0fLOArxO5LqtQ%3D&h=6829a30e\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/L8xy93I3hwk</a>"}]}